

                               MOGAL ChangeLog


Version 0.12.2, February 2021
 * Bugfix: a random number apparently could cause an out of bounds index

Version 0.12.1, September 2020
 * Bugfix in message passing, message is now split in 64k parts

Version 0.12.0, May 2018
 * A genetic algorithm factory can now send messages which are delivered
   to the genetic algorithm instance that started the optimization.

Version 0.11.0, November 2016
 * In case a multi-objective algorithm is used, but the number of fitness
   components is one, the (faster) routines from the single-objective
   version are used.

Version 0.10.1, February 2016
 * Small adjustment in setting some socket options. Now also compiles on 
   OS X.

Version 0.10.0, July 2012
 * Fixed small bug in error message in GeneticAlgorithm. Occurred
   when connection to gaserver failed.
 * Added faster non-dominated sort routine
 * Added CUDA based non-dominated sort routine (by default disabled
   now, needs more testing)
 * Switched to CMake build system
 * Should be possible to build on an MS-Windows platform as well now.
 * Added support for MPI.
 * Added DoubleVectorGenome and factory. Can be a good starting point
   to develop your own GA.

Version 0.9.0, May 2008
 * Initial public release

